[Results from the BT reference laboratory (IAH, Pirbright, UK) are anticipated. In particular, it will be interesting to obtain genotyping results and confirmation -- or otherwise -- of earlier assumption that the virus might be of vaccine origin (Russian press release 20121126.1424954).

Until an official confirmation is obtained or results from the reference laboratory become available, the described cases, in 4 countries, are regarded as 'suspected.' - Mod.AS

